/*
TODO:

- Modal movement layer.
    - Instead of holding, you press once and it's enabled.
    - Add deletion sub-layer
    - Add selection sub-layer
- Consider having the bluetooth keys as a long hold on the base layer.
- Consider using the accent key as a modifier.
- Consider using the dash key as a modifier.
